The assassination of Charlie Kirk is a tragic example of the rising acceptance of political violence in our nation. His death should serve as a clarion call for all Americans to reject hatred and denounce any celebration of death for political gain.

We pray for Charlie Kirk, his wife and their family as we await updates on his condition.
